==English==
'''sabbatical'''

===Adjective===
#Relating to the [[Sabbath]].
#Relating to a sabbatical (''see noun'').

====Translations====
*French: [[sabbatique]] (1)
*Italian: [[sabbatico]] (2)

===Noun===
#An extended period of [[leave#Noun|leave]] taken in order to carry out other projects. [[university|University]] [[lecturer]]s, for example, may be granted a one-year sabbatical once every seven years. 

